title: Keke Challenge Gone Wrong
warning: sensitive content: contains graphic content and may disturb some viewers
shortDescription: Fortunately, this video does not capture a woman actually being hit by a car while performing the Keke challenge.
longDescription: This video was originally posted to Instagram by user @lofi3D on 21 July 2018. However, many viewers encountered this video on YouTube or other social media platforms, where it was presented without that post’s disclaimer stating that the video was “NOT REAL” and that the footage had been edited. More details at: https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/keke-challenge-gone-wrong/
